                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1950" notAfter="1973">Second half of the 20th cent. The
                        Ms. has been paid and then donated to Qarsabar Mikāʾel in 1966 A.M. (=
                        1973/74 A.D.) (s. Additiones 1-2). The dates 1965 A.M. (= 1972/73 A.D.) and
                        1973 are written after the text of the Nicene Creed on <locus target="#60r">60r</locus>) in European numerals.</origDate>
                  </origin>
               <provenance>Additiones 1 and 2 mention wayzaro Bǝrritu as the donor. Elsewhere, ʾabuna Kidāna Māryām, Walatta Ṣādǝqān, Gabra
                     ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer are mentioned (s. 59vb).</provenance></history>
